Class SumoAmbassador

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.rti.api.AbstractFederateAmbassador
org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.sumo.ambassador.AbstractSumoAmbassador
org.eclipse.mosaic.fed.sumo.ambassador.SumoAmbassador
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<FederateAmbassador>, EventProcessor, FederateAmbassador
Direct Known Subclasses:
LibSumoAmbassador, SumoGuiAmbassador
public class SumoAmbassador extends AbstractSumoAmbassador
Implementation of a AbstractSumoAmbassador for the traffic simulator SUMO. It allows to control the progress of the traffic simulation and publishes VehicleUpdates.
